{"id":579876,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/03/知乎：如果司机疲劳驾驶不换班，乘客怎么做？/","date":"2018-03-02T09:15:22Z","modified":"2018-03-02T16:24:26Z","title":"知乎：如果司机疲劳驾驶不换班，乘客怎么做？——下架！","content":"<p>3月2日消息，今天北京网信办发布紧急通知。“知乎”平台因管理不严，传播违法违规信息，根据相关法律法规，要求各应用商店下架“知乎”App七天。具体时间从今天15时开始，至3月9日15时恢复。</p>\n<blockquote><p><strong>相关阅读：中国数字空间｜</strong><strong><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/space/%E6%96%B0%E6%B5%AA%E5%BE%AE%E5%8D%9A%E6%95%8F%E6%84%9F%E8%AF%8D\">敏感词库</a></strong></p></blockquote>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-579888\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/IMG_4337-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"711\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/IMG_4337-169x300.jpg 169w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/IMG_4337.jpg 450w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" /></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/1519981053675.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-579877\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/1519981053675.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"710\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/1519981053675.jpg 500w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/1519981053675-169x300.jpg 169w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" /></a></p>\n<p>财经网科技第一时间向知乎方面确认，知乎方面表示“将尽快调整上架”。财经网科技在安卓应用商店搜索“知乎”发现，页面显示知乎因违规下架。但是苹果APP Store中搜索“知乎”则仍然存在。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/1519981097484.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-579878\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/1519981097484.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"710\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/1519981097484.jpg 500w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/1519981097484-169x300.jpg 169w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" /></a></p>\n<p>知乎方面向财经网科技表示，已经下载使用知乎APP的用户不受此次调整影响。</p>\n<p><strong>附：知乎已经很努力了</strong></p>\n<div id=\"attachment_579880\" style=\"width: 510px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/知乎袁世凯.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-579880\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/知乎袁世凯.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"327\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/知乎袁世凯.jpg 1562w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/知乎袁世凯-300x196.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/知乎袁世凯-768x502.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/知乎袁世凯-1024x670.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/知乎袁世凯-230x150.jpg 230w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080\">知乎问题页面截图</span></p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_579879\" style=\"width: 410px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/知乎2.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-579879\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/知乎2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"711\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/知乎2.jpg 1152w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/知乎2-169x300.jpg 169w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/知乎2-768x1365.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/知乎2-576x1024.jpg 576w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080\">微博图片</span></p></div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<blockquote><p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/知乎.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-579881\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/知乎.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"711\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/知乎.jpg 720w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/知乎-169x300.jpg 169w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/知乎-576x1024.jpg 576w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" /></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p></blockquote>\n","author":980,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,19168,20534],"tags":[31267,9553,27058,25052,8616,9212]}